PrecisAppointment of an ADMINISTRATOR of the Government of NEWFOUNDLAND, namely the Hon. JAMES R. GUSHUE, who shall execute the office and functions of the Lieutenant Governor from November 6 to November 10, 1995, during the absence, illness or other inability of the latter.
